com.androidanimator.demo

Class AnimationDetailActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.androidanimator.demo.AnimationDetailActivity

  • public class AnimationDetailActivity
extends Activity
    An activity representing a single Animation detail screen. This activity is only used on phones. On tablets, item details are presented side-by-side with a list of items in a AnimationListActivity.

    This activity is mostly just a 'shell' activity containing nothing more than a AnimationDetailFragment.
